<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٨٩ - نا ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ , عَنْ عَمْرٍو , عَنِ الْحَسَنِ ,<span class="c5"> أَنَّهُ قَرَأَ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَيُحَذِّرُكُمُ اللَّهُ نَفْسَهُ , وَاللَّهُ رَءُوفٌ بِالْعِبَادِ}</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«مِنْ رَأْفَتِهِ بِهِمْ أَنْ حَذَّرَهُمُ نَفْسَهُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>